graphql.query:
mutation createNonFunctionalConcern ($input: CreateNonFunctionalConcernInput!) {
    createNonFunctionalConcern (input: $input) {
        id
        scenario
        metric
        qualityAttribute {
            id
            name
            description
            nonFunctionalConcern {
                id
                scenario
                metric
                qualityAttribute {
                    id
                    name
                    description
                    createdAt
                    updatedAt
                    qualityAttributeNonFunctionalConcernId
                }
                designDecisionID
                createdAt
                updatedAt
                nonFunctionalConcernQualityAttributeId
            }
            createdAt
            updatedAt
            qualityAttributeNonFunctionalConcernId
        }
        designDecisionID
        createdAt
        updatedAt
        nonFunctionalConcernQualityAttributeId
    }
}

query getDesignDecision ($id: ID!) {
    getDesignDecision (id: $id) {
      id
      name
      description
      context {
        id
        requirementRef
        description
        componentRef
        designDecision {
          id
          name
          description
          parentDesignDecisionID
          createdAt
          updatedAt
          designDecisionContextId
          designDecisionMetadataId
        }
        createdAt
        updatedAt
        contextDesignDecisionId
      }
      metadata {
        id
        reporterName
        sourceRef
        designDecision {
          id
          name
          description
          parentDesignDecisionID
          createdAt
          updatedAt
          designDecisionContextId
          designDecisionMetadataId
        }
        createdAt
        updatedAt
        metadataDesignDecisionId
      }
      nonFunctionalConcerns {
        items {
          id
          scenario
          metric
          designDecisionID
          createdAt
          updatedAt
          nonFunctionalConcernQualityAttributeId
        }
        nextToken
      }
      consequences {
        items {
          id
          description
          impact
          designDecisionID
          createdAt
          updatedAt
        }
        nextToken
      }
      alternatives {
        items {
          id
          description
          name
          designDecisionID
          createdAt
          updatedAt
        }
        nextToken
      }
      artifacts {
        items {
          id
          name
          description
          url
          designDecisionID
          createdAt
          updatedAt
        }
        nextToken
      }
      related {
        items {
          id
          name
          description
          parentDesignDecisionID
          createdAt
          updatedAt
          designDecisionContextId
          designDecisionMetadataId
        }
        nextToken
      }
      parentDesignDecisionID
      parentDesignDecision {
        id
        name
        description
        context {
          id
          requirementRef
          description
          componentRef
          createdAt
          updatedAt
          contextDesignDecisionId
        }
        metadata {
          id
          reporterName
          sourceRef
          createdAt
          updatedAt
          metadataDesignDecisionId
        }
        createdAt
        updatedAt
        designDecisionContextId
        designDecisionMetadataId
      }
      createdAt
      updatedAt
      designDecisionContextId
      designDecisionMetadataId
    }
}
